      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以TransactionQueue是入口，Lobby是第一个状态。Host Starts这个事件会让Lobby转到GameStarted对吧？我注意到您提到了Host角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Lobby",
        "GameStarted",
        "Host Starts"
