    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Host Starts触发GameStarted。然后需要Init Question进入QuestionPrep，这是出题准备阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GameStarted",
        "Init Question",
        "QuestionPrep"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上这条线。接下来QuestionPrep应该由Host Shows触发到QuestionActive，进入答题状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QuestionPrep",
        "Host Shows",
        "QuestionActive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。关键是AnswerValidation这个状态，Player Buzzes触发进入。这里要分叉：Correct Answer回到QuestionPrep继续下一题，Wrong Answer回到QuestionActive让其他人抢答。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AnswerValidation",
        "Player Buzzes",
        "Correct Answer",
        "Wrong Answer",
        "QuestionPrep",
        "QuestionActive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，AnswerValidation有两个出口。那游戏结束呢？Host应该能随时终止吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AnswerValidation",
        "Host"
