    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Host Ends从QuestionPrep直接跳到GameOver。最后GameOver要连到FinTech_AuthVault做结算，这是和入口对应的出口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QuestionPrep",
